{
  "stem": "20084.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyhow, then we saw men on horses, the SS on horses, on tall horses with their feet practically touching the ground, so big guys, like superior guys, you know, showing that strength, marching through the-- through the-- through the [INAUDIBLE], through the town.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is a terrific to a kid, made a terrific, psychologically impression, you know, how-- how powerful they are, how strong and big, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But anyhow, then-- then right away, they issue a proclamation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then a couple of weeks later or what, in Polish and in German, that all of the Jews have to be identified.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they cannot do this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They cannot do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they have to wear armbands.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And especially, they started off with the Jews who they could identify, the Orthodox Jews with the beard, who wore difference black, black hats and black-- they started grabbing them on the street, beating them up, taking pair of scissors and cutting off their beards, and pulling-- ripping out the beards.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And started-- started a lot of trouble.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we had opened the business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Germans-- the business was open.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That guy I worked for on [INAUDIBLE], it was the name was Haber.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had a dry goods store.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Ha, didn't take long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Germans came in and were buying materials, whatever they could.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were shipping it to Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And didn't last long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this-- the job ended, I think, because they run out of-- of products in the-- of materials, whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they used to-- then they used to come with the-- with-- trucks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They used to grab us on the streets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And because we wore our armbands and-- and load us on trucks.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
